author: Russell Brand
description:
The clip explores Dr John Campbell’s claim that early vaccine deaths were statistically hidden by classifying the recently vaccinated as “unvaccinated,” artificially inflating death rates in that group and shaping the narrative of risk. He argues that the one decisive data point — participant-level records linking vaccination status to excess deaths — is being withheld by governments despite glimpses from abroad suggesting uncomfortable correlations, raising profound questions about transparency, consent, and the management of public perception.
